# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Hippocampus Pipeline – Environment Configuration
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# This file is read by Docker Compose.  Host filesystem mounts are
# configured automatically by the startup scripts:
#
#   Windows:      .\start.ps1
#   Linux/macOS:  ./start.sh
#
# The scripts generate docker-compose.override.yml with the correct
# volume mounts for your system.  You should not need to edit this
# file unless you want to override specific environment variables.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
